  • Method Details

    • place

      public boolean place​(Orders order)
      The passed in dish gets placed on the counter and is stored there. If there is already a dish on the counter, the new dish will not be placed and old dish will stay there.
      Parameters:
      order - the dish that is getting placed on the counter
      Returns:
      returns true if the dish is successfully placed (nothing already on the counter), false otherwise

    • pickUp

      public Orders pickUp()
      The dish that was on the counter is taken off the counter.
      Returns:
      the dish that is on the counter (null is returned if nothing was on the table)
